reviewText: This box set has a lot of action in it, a lot of battles. If your a bit sad that Aizen was defeated in the previous box set, then watch this one, it's kinda fun to watch.
This is probably the best of the filler seasons. And personally the best episodes of this arc are all in the begining that you get in this dvd set.

This will be covering the start of a filler season (Not a story from the original manga books) written by the anime writers themselves, which normally would be horrible, think of the Bounts, The New Captain arc, the Zanpakuto Alternate tale which was decent, but I thought this filler season was actually pretty good.  It mainly features clones of the Soul Reaper captains and Lieutenants so you get to eventually see Kenpachi fight Kenpachi, Byakuya fight Byakuya, Byakuya fight Hitsugaya, and so on.  The real story doesn't continue until the final season ending in episode 366.
